OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after
OL,7,Fshots were fired at a man on a street
OL,8,Fin Leigh.
OL,10,FA gunman opened fire on Kenwood
OL,11,FAvenue, at the junction with St
OL,12,FAndrew's Drive, at around 11pm on
OL,13,FFriday 15 May.
OL,15,FA man, aged in his 40s, was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital with gunshot wounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
