OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,FPolice said his injuries are
OL,7,Fthankfully not thought to be life-
OL,8,Fthreatening or life-changing. The
OL,9,Fsuspect ran from the scene towards
OL,10,FManchester Road.
OL,12,FNo arrests have been made, a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice said.
OL,16,FDetectives stressed the shooting
OL,17,Foutside a property was believed to be
OL,18,F'isolated'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
