OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,FInvestigations are now underway on the
OL,7,Fscene. St Andrew's Drive has been
OL,8,Fcordoned off at the junction with
OL,9,FKenwood Avenue.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Sarah Bell,
OL,12,Ffrom GMP's Wigan and Leigh district,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are investigating a firearms
OL,14,Fdischarge that occurred overnight, and
OL,15,FI want to reassure the community in
OL,16,Fthe local area that this appears to be
OL,17,Fan isolated incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
