OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779117069
OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,F"I understand that incidents of this
OL,7,Fnature can cause concern among
OL,8,Fresidents and since it occurred, we
OL,9,Fhave taken all steps necessary to keep
OL,10,Four investigation moving at pace. We
OL,11,Fhave increased our presence in the
OL,12,Farea also with officers out on patrol.
OL,13,FThey are there for your safety but
OL,14,Fplease speak to them if you have any
OL,15,Fconcerns at all or information that
OL,16,Fmight help with our investigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
