OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779117069
OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,F"This type of criminality does not
OL,7,Fbelong on our streets. People should
OL,8,Fbe safe and well in their own homes
OL,9,Fand we will be doing everything we can
OL,10,Fto bring those responsible to justice."
OL,12,FPolice want to speak to anyone with
OL,13,Finformation about the shooting. They
OL,14,Falso want to speak to anyone with any
OL,15,Fdoorbell, CCTV or dash cam footage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
