OL,3,CInvestigation underway after shots
OL,4,Cfired at man outside home
OL,6,FGMP can be contacted via 101 quoting
OL,7,Flog 3830 of 15.05.2026. The Live Chat
OL,8,Fservice is also available and can be
OL,9,Ffound at gmp.police.uk. Alternatively,
OL,10,Fyou can report anonymously to
OL,11,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 1111.
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
